        <h2>2. Restrictions</h2>
        <p>You may not: (a) redistribute or resell this Agent Kit or its contents; (b) use this Agent Kit's contents to train, fine-tune, or evaluate machine learning models without explicit written permission from the publisher; (c) reverse engineer or extract components for use outside their intended purpose without permission.</p>

        <h2>3. Attribution</h2>
        <p>If you share outputs or derivatives of work performed using this Agent Kit, you must provide reasonable attribution to the original Kit Publisher.</p>

