        <h2>7. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>This Agreement is governed by applicable law. Disputes shall be resolved through good-faith negotiation before any formal proceeding.</p>

        <h2>8. Contact</h2>
        <p>For licensing questions, contact the Kit Publisher directly, or reach AgentKitProject at <a href="mailto:hello@agentkit-project.com">hello@agentkit-project.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .template-notice {
    background: #fef9c3;
    border: 1px solid #fde047;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    color: #713f12;
  }
  .legal-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .legal-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
</style>
